comments.body:
`m_connect_block_view` isn‚Äôt an empty view of the UTXO set - it's just a sandbox, a scratch space for `ConnectBlock()`. Consider rewording to avoid implying it has no backing state.

```suggestion
    //! Temporary `CCoinsViewCache` layered on top of `m_cacheview` and passed to `ConnectBlock()`.
    //! Reset between calls and flushed only on success, so invalid blocks don't pollute the underlying cache.
```

